00:21:04,290 --> 00:21:05,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, see ya.</font>

306
00:21:05,780 --> 00:21:07,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you so much for your help.</font>

307
00:21:08,340 --> 00:21:10,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't get caught by any 
more bad people, okay?</font>

308
00:21:15,290 --> 00:21:17,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were without sin, 
and I tried to kill you.</font>

309
